(73, 39, 16, 'Control Freak Eyebrow Gel', 'Out of control brows have you flustered? NYX Professional Makeup\'s Control Freak Brow Gel offers a new way to tame them fast. The clear formula works well over powder or pencil to seal the deal and make a statement with your brows that you will be proud of. The unique non-sticky formula is comfortable to wear all day and can also be used as a clear mascara that defines, separates and enhances the natural curl of lashes.', 6.00, 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dwdf8d06a2/ProductImages/Eyes/Control_Freak_Eyebrow_Gel/controlfreakeyebrowgel_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', 50),
