(310, 18, 16, 'All-In-Brow 3D', 'Inspired by the expert techniques of professional fashion show makeup artists, Dior presents its first eyebrow kit, which includes:', 43.00, 'https://www.dior.com/beauty/version-5.1432748111912/resize-image/ep/0/390/100/0/packshots%252FPDG_y0929580_f092958001.jpg', 50),
