(534, 43, 15, 'Physicians Formula Mineral Wear Airbrushing Blush', 'Physicians Formula Mineral Wear Airbrushing Blush is an ultra-fine mineral blush delivers a radiant pop of color with a flawless airbrushed finish.Directions: Buff on blush over cheekbones to define and contour or apply right below cheekbones for amore defined and dramatic look. For the most even application, be sure to tap excess powder from brush before applying.Ingredients: Mica, Boron Nitride, Zinc Stearate, Lauroyl Lysine, Tricaprylin, Magnesium Silicate, Camellia Oleifera Leaf Extract, Chamomilla Recutita (Matricaria) Flower Extract, Ginkgo Biloba Leaf Extract, Panax Ginseng Root Extract, Carthamus Tinctorius (Safflower) Seed Oil, Tocopheryl Acetate, Retinyl Palmitate, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Chlorphenesin, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Dehydroacetate, May Contain: Iron Oxides, Titanium Dioxide, Zinc OxideHypoallergenic. Fragrance-Free. Paraben-Free. Gluten Free. Dermatologist approved. Non-Comedogenic.', 15.49, 'https://d3t32hsnjxo7q6.cloudfront.net/i/e096eb4264561b76a90a9a2bfb6cfca2_ra,w158,h184_pa,w158,h184.jpeg', 50),
