(764, 54, 10, 'Suncoat Sugar-based Natural Liquid Eyeliner', 'This natural liquid eyeliner is made with natural sugar-based biopolymer, not synthetic plastics such as PVP (polyvinyl pyrrolidone polymer) and acrylic copolymer. Colored with earth pigments and enriched with vitamin E. This is a superior alternative for your sensitive eyes and our environment!Features: Natural and vegan ingredients, readily biodegradableStays on all day long, will not smear or smudgeKind to sensitive eyesRemove with soap and waterThe wand has a rubber tip instead of hairbrush, much easier to apply. It offers precise control for fine linesIngredients: Aqua (water), kaolin clay, glycerin, hydrolyzed Zea mays (corn) starch (natural multi-sugar resin), lecithin, Citrus grandis (grapefruit) seed extract, tocopherol (vitamin E), citric acid, iron oxides, mica, titanium dioxide.', 16.99, 'https://d3t32hsnjxo7q6.cloudfront.net/i/fffdf1e1c3948940e37d5b304275c0bd_ra,w158,h184_pa,w158,h184.jpeg', 50),
