(766, 1, 10, 'Almay Liquid Liner', 'Get beautiful definition with this easy-to-use liquid liner. Water-resistant formula lasts up to 16 hours without irritation. Unique \"inkwell\" design delivers fresh liquid liner for each application. Flexible-tip applicator provides mistake-proof control. Hypoallergenic Non-irritating Ophthalmologist, clinically and allergy tested Suitable for contact lens wearers', 10.99, 'https://d3t32hsnjxo7q6.cloudfront.net/i/e66b09555d41920597781babffee41dc_ra,w158,h184_pa,w158,h184.jpeg', 50),
